[{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_001","question":"在Excel中，以下哪个函数用于在表格首列中垂直查找数据？","options":["A. HLOOKUP","B. VLOOKUP","C. LOOKUP","D. XLOOKUP"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"VLOOKUP（Vertical Lookup）用于在表格首列中垂直查找指定值，返回该行中指定列的值。HLOOKUP是水平查找。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":1,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_002","question":"VLOOKUP函数的第四个参数设为FALSE表示什么？","options":["A. 近似匹配","B. 模糊查找","C. 精确匹配","D. 不区分大小写"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"VLOOKUP第四个参数为FALSE（或0）表示精确匹配。TRUE表示近似匹配。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":2,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_003","question":"以下哪个函数可以根据指定条件对区域中的数值求和？","options":["A. SUM","B. COUNT","C. SUMIF","D. AVERAGE"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"SUMIF根据指定条件对满足条件的单元格求和。SUM是无条件求和。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":3,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_004","question":"IF函数的正确语法是什么？","options":["A. IF(条件,假值,真值)","B. IF(值,条件,返回值)","C. IF(条件,真值,假值)","D. IF(返回值,条件,真值)"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"IF(条件, 条件为真时的值, 条件为假时的值)。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":4,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_005","question":"以下哪个函数用于统计包含数字的单元格个数？","options":["A. COUNTA","B. COUNT","C. COUNTIF","D. COUNTBLANK"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"COUNT统计数字个数。COUNTA统计非空，COUNTIF按条件。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":5,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_006","question":"在Excel中，符号$A$1表示什么类型的引用？","options":["A. 相对引用","B. 混合引用","C. 绝对引用","D. 循环引用"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"$A$1是绝对引用，复制公式时行列都不会变。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":6,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_007","question":"COUNTIF函数的作用是什么？","options":["A. 统计所有单元格","B. 按条件统计个数","C. 统计空单元格","D. 按条件求和"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"COUNTIF统计满足条件的单元格个数。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":7,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_008","question":"以下哪个函数可以将多个文本字符串合并为一个？","options":["A. TEXT","B. CONCATENATE","C. LEFT","D. TRIM"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"CONCATENATE（或&）用于合并多个文本字符串。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":8,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_009","question":"AVERAGE函数计算的是什么？","options":["A. 最大值","B. 最小值","C. 总和","D. 算术平均值"],"correctIndex":3,"explanation":"AVERAGE计算算术平均值。MAX返回最大值，MIN返回最小值。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":9,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_010","question":"若A1=5, B1=3, 则公式 =IF(A1>B1, \"大于\", \"不大于\") 的返回值是？","options":["A. 5","B. 3","C. 大于","D. 不大于"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"5>3条件为真，IF返回第二个参数\"大于\"。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":10,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_011","question":"SUMIFS函数与SUMIF函数的主要区别是什么？","options":["A. SUMIFS可指定多个条件","B. SUMIFS只能求和不能计数","C. SUMIFS速度更快","D. 没有区别"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"SUMIFS支持多个条件求和，SUMIF只支持单一条件。","difficulty":2,"orderIndex":11,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_012","question":"以下哪个可以正确地在单元格A1中显示今天的日期？","options":["A. =NOW()","B. =TODAY()","C. =DATE()","D. =DAY()"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"TODAY()返回当前日期。NOW()带时间。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":12,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_013","question":"LEFT函数的作用是什么？","options":["A. 从文本右侧截取字符","B. 删除文本左侧空格","C. 从文本左侧截取指定数量字符","D. 将文本转为大写"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"LEFT从文本左侧截取指定数量字符。RIGHT从右边截取。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":13,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_014","question":"数据透视表的主要功能是什么？","options":["A. 美化表格外观","B. 快速汇总和分析大量数据","C. 创建图表","D. 保护工作表"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"数据透视表可快速分类汇总和交叉分析大量数据。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":14,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_015","question":"如何快速将A列和B列的数据合并到C列（中间用空格分隔）？","options":["A. C1 = A1 + B1","B. C1 = A1 & \" \" & B1","C. C1 = MERGE(A1, B1)","D. C1 = COMBINE(A1, B1)"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"用&连接文本，空格用引号包裹。MERGE和COMBINE不是Excel函数。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":15,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_016","question":"若要在公式中固定引用B列（列不变行可变），正确的写法是？","options":["A. B1","B. $B$1","C. $B1","D. B$1"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"$B1列绝对引用（固定），行相对引用（可变）。","difficulty":2,"orderIndex":16,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_017","question":"ROUND函数的作用是？","options":["A. 向上取整","B. 向下取整","C. 四舍五入到指定小数位","D. 去掉小数部分"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"ROUND四舍五入到指定小数位。ROUNDUP向上，ROUNDDOWN向下。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":17,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_018","question":"以下哪个是条件格式的功能？","options":["A. 将单元格内容加粗","B. 根据条件自动设置颜色等格式","C. 限制用户输入内容","D. 保护单元格不被修改"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"条件格式根据值自动应用颜色等格式。数据验证用于限制输入。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":18,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_019","question":"VLOOKUP的第一个参数查找值必须在查找区域的哪一列？","options":["A. 任意列","B. 最后一列","C. 第一列","D. 中间列"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"VLOOKUP查找值必须在表格区域第一列。可用INDEX+MATCH从右向左查。","difficulty":2,"orderIndex":19,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_020","question":"以下哪个快捷键可以在Excel中快速插入当前日期？","options":["A. Ctrl + C","B. Ctrl + ;","C. Ctrl + D","D. Ctrl + T"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"Ctrl+;插入静态当前日期。Ctrl+Shift+;插入当前时间。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":20,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_021","question":"INDEX+MATCH组合函数相比VLOOKUP的优势是什么？","options":["A. 运算速度更快","B. 可以从右向左查找","C. 语法更简单","D. 不需要排序"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"INDEX+MATCH可从右向左查找，也能在插入删除列时保持稳定。","difficulty":2,"orderIndex":21,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_022","question":"以下哪个函数用于去除文本中多余的空格？","options":["A. CLEAN","B. TRIM","C. UPPER","D. PROPER"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"TRIM去除首尾空格和中间多余空格。CLEAN去除非打印字符。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":22,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_023","question":"在Excel中，公式 =SUM(A1:A10, C1:C10) 计算的是什么？","options":["A. A1到C10区域的总和","B. A1到A10的总和","C. A1:A10和C1:C10的总和","D. A1到A10减去C1到C10"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"SUM可接受多个参数，逗号分隔，计算所有参数的总和。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":23,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_024","question":"LEN函数的作用是什么？","options":["A. 截取文本","B. 返回文本长度（字符数）","C. 查找字符位置","D. 替换文本"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"LEN返回字符串字符个数。中英文都算1个。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":24,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_025","question":"以下关于数据验证的说法，哪个是正确的？","options":["A. 数据验证可以防止公式错误","B. 数据验证可以限制用户输入的类型和范围","C. 数据验证等同于密码保护","D. 数据验证只能用于数字"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"数据验证可限制整数、小数、日期、列表等输入类型。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":25,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_026","question":"以下哪个公式可以正确计算A1:A10区域中大于60的数值的平均值？","options":["A. =AVERAGEIF(A1:A10,\">60\")","B. =AVERAGE(A1:A10,\">60\")","C. =SUMIF(A1:A10,\">60\")/COUNT(A1:A10)","D. =MEANIF(A1:A10,\">60\")"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"AVERAGEIF按条件计算平均值。AVERAGE没有条件参数。","difficulty":2,"orderIndex":26,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_027","question":"在Excel中，合并单元格后，合并区域中的数据会怎样？","options":["A. 所有单元格数据保留","B. 只保留拼接后的数据","C. 只保留左上角单元格的数据","D. 所有数据被清空"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"合并单元格后只保留左上角第一个单元格的数据。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":27,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_028","question":"MAX函数与LARGE函数的区别是什么？","options":["A. 没有区别","B. MAX返回最大值，LARGE可返回第N大的值","C. MAX只能用于数字，LARGE可用于文本","D. LARGE返回最大值，MAX返回最小值"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"LARGE(array,k)返回第k大值。SMALL返回第k小值。","difficulty":2,"orderIndex":28,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_029","question":"以下哪个是绝对引用和相对引用混合的正确示例？","options":["A. =A1+B1","B. =$A$1+$B$1","C. =$A1+B$1","D. =##A1+##B1"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"$A1列固定行可变，B$1行固定列可变。","difficulty":2,"orderIndex":29,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"excel","questionId":"excel_030","question":"以下哪个快捷键可以快速选中整张工作表？","options":["A. Ctrl + A","B. Ctrl + S","C. Ctrl + Z","D. Ctrl + X"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"Ctrl+A选中全部。再按一次选中整张表。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":30,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_001","question":"Python中如何输出Hello World？","options":["A. console.log(\"Hello World\")","B. print(\"Hello World\")","C. echo \"Hello World\"","D. System.out.println(\"Hello World\")"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"Python使用print()函数输出。console.log是JavaScript。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":1,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_002","question":"以下哪个是Python中的列表（list）？","options":["A. (1, 2, 3)","B. {1, 2, 3}","C. [1, 2, 3]","D. <1, 2, 3>"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"[1,2,3]是列表。(1,2,3)是元组，{1,2,3}是集合。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":2,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_003","question":"以下代码输出什么？print(type(3.14))","options":["A. <class int>","B. <class float>","C. <class str>","D. <class bool>"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"3.14是浮点数（float），type()返回其类型。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":3,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_004","question":"以下哪个变量命名是合法的？","options":["A. 2name","B. my-name","C. _count","D. class"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"_count合法。2name不能数字开头，my-name含非法字符，class是关键字。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":4,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_005","question":"len([1, 2, 3, 4, 5]) 的返回值是？","options":["A. 4","B. 5","C. 15","D. 1"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"len()返回元素个数，有5个元素所以返回5。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":5,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_006","question":"以下哪个方法可以向列表末尾添加元素？","options":["A. list.add()","B. list.append()","C. list.insert()","D. list.push()"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"append()在末尾添加。insert()指定位置。add()是集合方法。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":6,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_007","question":"Python中用于循环的关键词是？","options":["A. loop","B. foreach","C. for","D. repeat"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"Python用for...in...遍历。while也可循环。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":7,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_008","question":"以下哪个是Python字典（dict）？","options":["A. [\"a\", \"b\"]","B. (\"a\", \"b\")","C. {\"a\", \"b\"}","D. {\"name\":\"张三\",\"age\":25}"],"correctIndex":3,"explanation":"{\"name\":\"张三\"}是字典。[\"a\",\"b\"]是列表，(\"a\",\"b\")是元组，{\"a\",\"b\"}是集合。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":8,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_009","question":"print(10 // 3) 输出什么？","options":["A. 3.333...","B. 3","C. 1","D. 3.0"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"//是整除运算符，10//3=3。10/3返回3.333，10%3返回1。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":9,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_010","question":"字符串方法 .strip() 的作用是什么？","options":["A. 删除中间空格","B. 删除两端空白字符","C. 分割为列表","D. 转为大写"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"strip()删除两端空白。split()分割，upper()转大写。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":10,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_011","question":"以下哪个是正确的函数定义？","options":["A. function myFunc():","B. def myFunc():","C. func myFunc():","D. define myFunc():"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"Python用def定义函数。function是JavaScript。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":11,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_012","question":"f-string（f\"...\"）的作用是什么？","options":["A. 格式化字符串嵌入变量","B. 表示函数","C. 表示文件路径","D. 表示浮点数"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"f-string在Python3.6+引入，用花括号嵌入变量值。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":12,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_013","question":"判断值是否在列表中，应该用哪个关键词？","options":["A. has","B. in","C. contains","D. exists"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"Python用in检查成员：if x in my_list。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":13,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_014","question":"print(3 == 3.0) 输出什么？","options":["A. True","B. False","C. 报错","D. None"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"==比较值相等，3和3.0值相等返回True。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":14,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_015","question":"range(5) 生成什么？","options":["A. [1,2,3,4,5]","B. (0,1,2,3,4,5)","C. 0到4的数字序列","D. 5个随机数"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"range(5)生成0,1,2,3,4（不包括5）。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":15,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_016","question":"以下哪个方法可以将字符串全部转为小写？","options":["A. .lowercase()","B. .toLower()","C. .lower()","D. .small()"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"lower()转全小写。upper()转全大写。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":16,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_017","question":"列表切片 [1,2,3,4,5][1:4] 返回什么？","options":["A. [1,2,3,4]","B. [2,3,4]","C. [2,3,4,5]","D. [1,2,3]"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"切片[start:end]包含start不包含end。索引1=2，索引4=5（不含）。","difficulty":2,"orderIndex":17,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_018","question":"关于元组（tuple）哪个说法正确？","options":["A. 元素可以修改","B. 是可变的","C. 是不可变的","D. 没有索引"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"元组是不可变数据类型，创建后不能修改。列表可变。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":18,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_019","question":"Python中如何导入math模块？","options":["A. include math","B. require math","C. import math","D. using math"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"Python用import导入：import math。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":19,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_020","question":"print(True and False) 输出什么？","options":["A. True","B. False","C. 1","D. 0"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"and两边为True才返回True。True and False返回False。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":20,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_021","question":"[x*2 for x in range(3)] 的结果是？","options":["A. [0,1,2]","B. [2,4,6]","C. [0,2,4]","D. [1,2,3]"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"range(3)生成0,1,2，每个×2得0,2,4。","difficulty":2,"orderIndex":21,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_022","question":"以下哪个可以正确读取文件内容？","options":["A. open(\"f.txt\",\"r\").read()","B. read(\"f.txt\")","C. file.read(\"f.txt\")","D. open.read(\"f.txt\")"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"open()打开文件，read()读取内容。推荐with语句。","difficulty":2,"orderIndex":22,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_023","question":"print(\"Python\"[0]) 输出什么？","options":["A. P","B. y","C. Python","D. 报错"],"correctIndex":0,"explanation":"字符串索引从0开始。\"Python\"[0]=P。[-1]=n。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":23,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_024","question":"异常处理中finally子句的作用？","options":["A. 只在异常时执行","B. 只在无异常时执行","C. 无论是否异常都执行","D. 终止程序"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"finally代码块无论是否异常都会执行，常用于释放资源。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":24,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_025","question":"列表方法 .pop() 的作用是？","options":["A. 在末尾添加元素","B. 删除并返回指定位置元素","C. 排序列表","D. 复制列表"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"pop()默认删除最后一个。append()添加，sort()排序。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":25,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_026","question":"以下哪个可以将\"1,2,3\"按逗号分割成列表？","options":["A. .cut(\",\")","B. .split(\",\")","C. .divide(\",\")","D. .separate(\",\")"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"split()按分隔符分割。join()是逆操作。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":26,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_027","question":"Python中None表示什么？","options":["A. 数字0","B. 空字符串","C. 空值/无值","D. False"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"None是空值，不等于0、空字符串或False。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":27,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_028","question":"以下哪个会导致报错？my_dict={\"a\":1,\"b\":2}; print(my_dict[\"c\"])","options":["A. my_dict[\"a\"]","B. my_dict.get(\"c\")","C. my_dict[\"c\"]","D. 都不会报错"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"用[]访问不存在的键会报KeyError。.get()返回None不报错。","difficulty":2,"orderIndex":28,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_029","question":"以下哪种写法可以正确创建包含0到9的列表？","options":["A. list(0,9)","B. list(range(10))","C. range.toList(10)","D. [0..9]"],"correctIndex":1,"explanation":"list(range(10))将range对象转为列表。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":29,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]},{"bankId":"python","questionId":"python_030","question":"Python中注释的正确写法是？","options":["A. // 注释","B. <!-- 注释 -->","C. # 注释","D. /* 注释 */"],"correctIndex":2,"explanation":"Python单行注释用#。多行用三个引号。//是Java注释。","difficulty":1,"orderIndex":30,"knowledgeIds":[],"codeBlocks":[]}]